      • saveAs

        public void saveAs()
        Saves the snapshot to an external (user defined) destination. Default implementation does nothing, custom implementations should open a Save File dialog and save the snapshot to selected destination. Throws an UnsupportedOperationException if supportsSaveAs() returns false.
